If I had trusted you more back then,

81
00:05:41,970 --> 00:05:43,780
maybe things wouldn't

82
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,380
be like this now.

83
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,350
I've also been thinking

84
