119
00:07:49,550 --> 00:07:50,890
I'm here to buy braised food.

120
00:07:50,890 --> 00:07:51,960
Since Grandma isn't here,

121
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:52,960
I'll leave.

122
00:07:53,130 --> 00:07:53,670
Bye bye.

123
