163
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:01,380
Mr. Dou,

164
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:03,340
I'm going with you.

165
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:05,180
If anything happens,

166
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,930
