167
00:11:07,970 --> 00:11:10,640
If you're going to let go, do it cleanly.

168
00:11:11,530 --> 00:11:12,460
No.

169
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:14,300
You saved me.

170
00:11:14,330 --> 00:11:16,260
My life is yours.

171
00:11:17,430 --> 00:11:19,120
