172
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:21,010
You have your own life.

173
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,800
Take care.

174
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:24,120
You two too.

175
00:11:26,310 --> 00:11:27,540
Mr. Dou.

176
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:31,490
Mr. Dou!

177
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:32,230
Boss!

178
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:33,660
Boss, don't leave us too.

179
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:34,960
Don't give up on us.

180
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,540
I won't leave you.

181
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,700
As long as I have a bite to eat,

182
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,010
you won't starve.

183
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:40,100
-Really?
-Really?

184
00:11:40,330 --> 00:11:41,170
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

185
00:11:41,170 --> 00:11:42,570
Boss, I love you the most.

186
00:12:31,410 --> 00:12:32,870
It's okay if you're drunk.

187
00:12:33,470 --> 00:12:34,810
You can rest at my place.

188
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:37,750
What do you want?

189
00:12:39,810 --> 00:12:43,000
To make the rumor going around
the Intelligence Bureau come true.

190
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,800
Do you agree?

191
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,600
Are you looking for a job?

192
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:25,430
Yes.

193
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:29,630
Are you trying to save money
to buy our home?

194
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:32,660
I want to pay back the money
I owe Mr. Dou as soon as I can

195
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:34,520
