196
00:13:40,290 --> 00:13:41,830
I'm Bai,

197
00:13:41,990 --> 00:13:44,040
but I'm not your toy boy.

198
00:13:44,070 --> 00:13:46,050
We agreed to work hard together.

199
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:47,650
Mm.

200
00:13:51,850 --> 00:13:53,680
Do you have any job in mind?

201
00:13:57,490 --> 00:13:59,810
I used to do errands
for the convenience house.

202
00:13:59,810 --> 00:14:00,710
Every time I saw

203
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:02,440
