204
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:05,350
I felt a real sense of achievement.

205
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:06,610
Too bad—

206
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:09,220
if only the convenience house

207
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,920
was just about simple errands

208
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:14,100
and not all that complicated stuff.

209
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,360
Yeah.

210
00:14:17,690 --> 00:14:20,160
If we could open one together,

211
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,460
