234
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:52,710
Why does this feel so familiar?

235
00:15:55,140 --> 00:15:56,950
Are you following me again?

236
00:15:58,340 --> 00:15:59,050
Yes.

237
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,620
I followed you here.

238
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:02,460
Because of this client?

239
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,520
This woman

240
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:05,980
has specifically requested you twice.

241
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:07,370
Who knows if she was just pretending

242
00:16:07,370 --> 00:16:08,880
to have a job for you

243
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:10,990
because she's actually interested in you?

244
00:16:10,990 --> 00:16:12,760
I already explained.

245
00:16:12,780 --> 00:16:13,840
Last time, I went shopping with her

246
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,640
to pick a gift for her boyfriend.

247
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:16,710
She wanted a man's opinion.

248
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:18,910
This time, she invited you to her place.

249
00:16:19,010 --> 00:16:20,350
