You look cute when you're jealous.

256
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,900
Trying to shut me up with a kiss?

257
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:45,870
I can kiss you too.

258
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:50,570
You want to do this, huh?

259
00:16:50,570 --> 00:16:51,640
Let's go home.

260
